WEBVTT

01:35.990 --> 01:41.270
[Pursuit of Jade]

01:41.380 --> 01:43.950
[Episode 6]

01:44.020 --> 01:47.259
[Xigu Lane]

01:57.590 --> 01:59.229
Zheng! Zheng!

01:59.530 --> 02:01.020
My sister is going to butcher  a pig.

02:01.020 --> 02:02.460
Come and watch.

02:02.870 --> 02:03.810
Butcher a pig?

02:09.630 --> 02:12.220
Don't move. I'll make it quick.

02:12.380 --> 02:13.950
You've been a good pig in this life.

02:13.950 --> 02:15.750
Be a good person in the next life!

02:16.750 --> 02:18.990
I feel like I've heard that somewhere.

02:20.010 --> 02:21.829
My sister is amazing, isn't she?

02:31.750 --> 02:32.400
Yan Zheng,

02:32.960 --> 02:34.560
take Changning inside.

02:34.630 --> 02:35.890
Don't let her see this.

02:36.140 --> 02:38.140
Or she'll have nightmares tonight.

02:38.840 --> 02:39.400
Okay.

02:40.360 --> 02:41.120
Let's go.

03:02.400 --> 03:03.260
Don't look.

03:08.360 --> 03:09.560
Don't be scared.

03:11.680 --> 03:13.120
I'm not scared of butchering pigs.

03:13.120 --> 03:15.280
I meant don't be scared of my sister.

03:40.240 --> 03:41.240
Do you need a hand?

03:47.020 --> 03:49.950
Did I scare you just now?

03:52.150 --> 03:54.200
If you were scared or disgusted,

03:54.400 --> 03:55.290
just say so.

03:55.360 --> 03:56.280
I'm used to it.

04:00.030 --> 04:01.300
I wasn't scared.

04:03.220 --> 04:04.620
Then you were disgusted.

04:11.420 --> 04:13.040
You didn't mind my injury.

04:13.750 --> 04:15.810
Why would I mind that you're capable?

04:30.300 --> 04:31.960
Stop looking. Go back inside.

04:35.760 --> 04:37.340
You should go inside and rest too.

04:37.340 --> 04:38.159
Stop adding wood.

04:38.159 --> 04:40.600
When scalding the pig bristles,
it smells terrible.

04:40.600 --> 04:41.920
This is nothing.

04:41.920 --> 04:43.720
I've smelled worse things.

04:43.990 --> 04:45.190
Like burning bodies.

04:48.000 --> 04:48.800
Right.

04:49.430 --> 04:50.830
You were an armed escort.

04:51.510 --> 04:53.240
You must have seen dead people.

05:32.909 --> 05:34.070
This pork—

05:34.159 --> 05:36.020
do you want me to hang it up for you?

05:36.510 --> 05:37.740
Hang on a second.

05:38.830 --> 05:39.870
This pork

05:40.120 --> 05:41.180
needs to be salted.

05:41.870 --> 05:42.560
Like this.

05:42.580 --> 05:44.850
Spread the salt evenly over the meat,

05:45.000 --> 05:47.260
let it cure for a few days,
then hang it up.

05:54.480 --> 05:55.140
Let me do it.

05:56.070 --> 05:56.870
I'll help you.

06:13.370 --> 06:15.870
My father and mother
used to make cured meat like this.

06:15.870 --> 06:17.200
They helped each other.

06:17.540 --> 06:18.680
Then what did you do?

06:19.940 --> 06:22.540
Changning and I
would make trouble on the side.

06:31.720 --> 06:34.350
This piece of pork is a bit too big.

06:34.510 --> 06:36.510
I need to make a few cuts
for the flavor to soak in.

06:36.510 --> 06:37.920
Pass me the knife.

07:04.600 --> 07:05.160
This one.

07:07.950 --> 07:08.920
This knife...

07:09.560 --> 07:10.820
where did it come from?

07:11.510 --> 07:13.170
My father had someone make it.

07:13.760 --> 07:16.490
Do you know what this knife is made of?

07:17.040 --> 07:18.040
Iron, obviously.

07:18.870 --> 07:20.530
What else could it be? Silver?

07:21.330 --> 07:22.530
But Father said that

07:23.430 --> 07:25.820
these two knives are our family heirlooms.

07:25.820 --> 07:27.680
They supported our whole family.

07:32.050 --> 07:33.909
Your father must have been quite skilled
in martial arts.

07:33.909 --> 07:35.240
Where did he learn that?

07:35.430 --> 07:37.750
He traveled extensively when he was young.

07:37.750 --> 07:40.070
Maybe he met some reclusive master.

08:18.360 --> 08:19.090
You won.

08:20.540 --> 08:22.220
Uncle, I won!

08:29.760 --> 08:31.270
You gained a slight advantage.

08:31.270 --> 08:33.419
Is it worth getting so excited?

08:33.840 --> 08:35.409
General He

08:35.429 --> 08:36.740
was just teasing you.

08:45.230 --> 08:45.780
This...

08:48.840 --> 08:50.630
This salt is very expensive.

08:51.510 --> 08:53.630
Why be stingy over a little salt?

08:55.150 --> 08:57.950
You don't run the house,
so you don't know the cost.

09:02.790 --> 09:05.080
Changyu, is the pig tail ready?

09:07.160 --> 09:09.610
I just put it in the pot.
It needs a while.

09:09.750 --> 09:10.360
Look.

09:12.980 --> 09:14.240
It's still early,

09:14.390 --> 09:16.120
and you're already craving it?

09:16.270 --> 09:17.200
Little glutton.

09:17.840 --> 09:19.030
I'm not a little glutton.

09:19.030 --> 09:20.300
Yes, you are.

09:24.240 --> 09:24.970
We caught it!

09:48.720 --> 09:49.780
What are you doing?

09:50.490 --> 09:52.870
I've seen this gyrfalcon
near our place several times.

09:52.870 --> 09:53.950
So I set a trap.

09:54.120 --> 09:56.180
I didn't expect to actually catch it.

09:59.090 --> 10:01.020
Little beast, you dared to bite me!

10:01.560 --> 10:03.550
I'll take you to the market tomorrow

10:03.550 --> 10:04.840
and sell you for ten taels of silver.

10:04.840 --> 10:05.910
At the market,

10:06.190 --> 10:08.320
few people buy live animals like this.

10:08.670 --> 10:09.960
Ordinary families can't tame them.

10:09.960 --> 10:11.910
These things are wild by nature

10:12.080 --> 10:13.410
and easily hurt people.

10:13.720 --> 10:15.120
That's a shame.

10:15.440 --> 10:16.750
Its wing is hurt too.

10:18.050 --> 10:19.050
How about...

10:19.320 --> 10:20.560
we just kill it

10:20.600 --> 10:22.060
and make some soup with it?

10:22.080 --> 10:23.480
Changning, turn around.

10:23.730 --> 10:24.620
No!

10:28.270 --> 10:29.270
I once...

10:30.000 --> 10:31.930
ate this kind of gyrfalcon's meat.

10:32.080 --> 10:34.390
It was tough and sour. Inedible.

10:36.040 --> 10:38.210
Don't worry. I'll cook it.

10:38.260 --> 10:40.700
Our brine could make a block of wood
taste good.

10:40.700 --> 10:41.470
No.

10:46.510 --> 10:49.550
Actually,
I know a little about taming birds.

10:49.790 --> 10:51.120
I can try to tame it.

10:51.590 --> 10:54.310
A tamed gyrfalcon
can sell for over 100 taels.

10:56.380 --> 10:57.660
Over 100 taels?

11:01.370 --> 11:02.930
That's worth way too much.

11:03.480 --> 11:04.750
Changning, get a chicken coop.

11:04.750 --> 11:05.510
Okay.

11:06.910 --> 11:08.770
Then I'll keep you at home for now,

11:08.950 --> 11:10.210
Little Hundred Taels.

11:18.550 --> 11:19.510
Stupid thing.

11:37.750 --> 11:38.810
What are you doing?

11:40.840 --> 11:42.240
I'm bandaging its wound.

11:43.080 --> 11:44.750
Why are you using this?

11:47.530 --> 11:49.780
What's wrong with using this cloth?

11:50.600 --> 11:52.460
This is the hair ribbon I gave you.

11:56.890 --> 11:58.950
I thought it was just a piece of cloth.

12:08.270 --> 12:10.520
Father, Mother, the year is ending.

12:11.670 --> 12:13.210
This is the New Year pig.

12:13.240 --> 12:14.450
Have a taste.

12:18.760 --> 12:21.220
Today is also the 3rd day
since I got married.

12:22.080 --> 12:23.240
My husband...

12:23.550 --> 12:26.320
He doesn't know
that salt should be used sparingly.

12:26.320 --> 12:28.120
But he helped me make cured meat.

12:28.830 --> 12:30.830
And he'd step forward to protect me.

12:34.150 --> 12:35.870
If your spirits are watching,

12:36.840 --> 12:39.730
please bless him with a quick recovery,

12:39.870 --> 12:41.000
and a peaceful life.

12:46.660 --> 12:47.780
As for Song Yan—

12:53.370 --> 12:54.610
that bastard—

12:55.440 --> 12:57.040
make sure he fails the exams.

13:04.870 --> 13:09.020
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

13:09.100 --> 13:13.020
[Tea] [Fan's Butcher Shop]

13:13.120 --> 13:16.510
[Guo Jiu's Butcher Shop] [Soup Noodles]

13:19.660 --> 13:24.630
[Butcher Shop]

13:24.950 --> 13:25.940
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

13:38.790 --> 13:42.070
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

13:42.600 --> 13:45.450
Who smashed my stuff?

13:45.210 --> 13:51.150
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

13:45.870 --> 13:48.360
Come out and face me if you have the guts!

13:48.860 --> 13:51.230
Hiding makes you a bastard!

13:53.480 --> 13:54.910
What are you looking at me for?

13:54.910 --> 13:56.640
I didn't do it.

13:57.080 --> 13:58.390
This is called...

13:58.480 --> 14:01.400
karma.

14:04.000 --> 14:05.240
Oh no, Changyu.

14:05.380 --> 14:07.810
Your shop was closed for almost 2 months.

14:08.000 --> 14:09.720
Did you forget
to pay the protection money?

14:09.660 --> 14:14.110
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

14:10.480 --> 14:12.140
What is the protection money?

14:14.270 --> 14:17.370
[Guo Jiu's Butcher Shop]

14:25.510 --> 14:27.440
You dare to keep running this shop?

14:27.870 --> 14:29.390
Aren't you afraid of death?

14:29.390 --> 14:31.790
I'd like to see who on this street

14:32.130 --> 14:33.900
dares not pay up.

14:35.400 --> 14:36.400
It's you.

14:37.520 --> 14:38.600
Turn around.

14:38.840 --> 14:40.480
I'm talking to you!

14:46.600 --> 14:47.180
Mrs...

14:47.360 --> 14:48.570
Mrs. Fan.

14:53.790 --> 14:56.540
This butcher shop is yours?

14:56.840 --> 14:57.480
Not bad.

14:58.760 --> 14:59.890
How much do you want?

15:00.000 --> 15:02.390
Misunderstanding.
It's all a misunderstanding.

15:02.390 --> 15:04.360
How could we ask you for protection money?

15:04.360 --> 15:04.870
Hey.

15:12.080 --> 15:12.750
Got it.

15:12.750 --> 15:14.090
Come on. Hurry up and fix it.

15:14.090 --> 15:16.070
[Meat]

15:14.320 --> 15:15.540
Fix it. Fix it.

15:19.120 --> 15:21.920
We're just doing a job we were paid for.

15:22.550 --> 15:23.720
Please don't mind.

15:23.720 --> 15:24.600
Who paid you?

15:27.920 --> 15:28.960
We're fixing your stove.

15:28.960 --> 15:30.200
So please don't ask.

15:31.080 --> 15:32.290
Although we are hooligans,

15:32.290 --> 15:34.820
we know the rule
about not betraying a client.

15:36.070 --> 15:37.180
Very loyal.

15:43.310 --> 15:45.440
The owner of Wang's Braised Meat Shop.

15:45.630 --> 15:46.390
Wang's?

15:48.400 --> 15:50.060
I have no grudge against them.

15:50.120 --> 15:50.790
I swear.

15:53.870 --> 15:56.000
You are... Mr. Jin, right?

15:56.000 --> 15:56.840
I am Jin Yuanbao.

15:56.840 --> 15:59.100
You can call me
Yuanbao or Bao from now on.

15:59.190 --> 16:01.860
[Meat]

15:59.440 --> 16:00.080
Don't just clean up here.

16:00.080 --> 16:02.210
Come on. Clean up inside too. Hurry up.

16:03.380 --> 16:05.560
Mandi, Mancang, Manwu.

16:06.390 --> 16:07.910
You can boss them around however you like.

16:07.910 --> 16:09.080
Are they all surnamed Man?

16:09.080 --> 16:09.960
I named them.

16:10.000 --> 16:11.120
My name is Jin Yuanbao,
which means money, right?

16:11.120 --> 16:13.320
So all their names mean "full of money."

16:13.360 --> 16:14.150
Fix it fast!

16:14.370 --> 16:15.900
I need to open for business.

16:16.110 --> 16:17.170
Open for business?

16:17.280 --> 16:18.240
Open for business?

16:18.240 --> 16:19.270
-You! Come here!
-Come here!

16:18.760 --> 16:20.650
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

16:19.320 --> 16:20.120
-Buy meat!
-Come here!

16:20.120 --> 16:20.840
You!

16:21.750 --> 16:24.040
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

16:22.340 --> 16:24.320
-I'm talking to you two!
-Come here.

16:24.320 --> 16:25.380
What are you doing?

16:25.480 --> 16:27.010
Forcing people to buy meat?

16:29.790 --> 16:31.020
Buy... Buy...

16:31.320 --> 16:32.320
Buy some pork!

16:31.850 --> 16:34.820
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

16:32.320 --> 16:32.960
Don't...

16:34.000 --> 16:34.890
Would you like to buy some?

16:34.890 --> 16:36.430
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

16:35.200 --> 16:36.460
Buy meat. Go. Go buy it.

16:36.510 --> 16:37.480
Come on. Come on.

16:36.580 --> 16:40.180
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

16:37.510 --> 16:38.550
-Come on.
-Buy some meat.

16:38.550 --> 16:39.150
Come on.

16:40.310 --> 16:42.520
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

16:43.390 --> 16:45.320
Just a little short of three taels.

17:03.480 --> 17:04.440
This meat is perfect for dumplings.

17:04.440 --> 17:06.300
Come back next time if you like it.

17:08.790 --> 17:09.750
Did you see that?

17:10.510 --> 17:11.750
That woman...

17:12.310 --> 17:14.069
can cast spells.

17:14.640 --> 17:15.880
Are you jealous

17:15.880 --> 17:17.069
or just envious?

17:17.069 --> 17:18.329
You have such a sharp tongue.

17:18.329 --> 17:19.810
Watch out for karma.

17:19.500 --> 17:22.560
[Guo Jiu's Butcher Shop]

17:20.069 --> 17:21.270
I neither steal nor rob.

17:21.270 --> 17:22.750
Why would karma find me?

17:23.069 --> 17:24.680
Keep an eye on your man.

17:24.680 --> 17:26.790
Then you'd better
keep an eye on your stove.

17:26.790 --> 17:28.240
Or it might get smashed.

17:32.880 --> 17:33.440
Okay.

17:33.830 --> 17:35.070
Come again next time.

17:35.710 --> 17:37.430
Pork!

17:38.850 --> 17:40.720
Pork!

17:42.830 --> 17:44.160
You little brat!

17:44.730 --> 17:46.520
I'll beat you to death!

17:46.880 --> 17:47.440
Grandma!

17:47.440 --> 17:48.240
Grandma, Grandma, Grandma.

17:48.240 --> 17:49.000
Wait, why are you here?

17:49.000 --> 17:49.720
-I'll kill you!
-Grandma! Grandma!

17:49.720 --> 17:50.920
Why are you hitting me?

17:50.920 --> 17:51.510
You...

17:52.070 --> 17:53.750
You're collecting protection money again!

17:53.750 --> 17:55.590
Why can't you change?

17:55.640 --> 17:56.590
I'm not collecting protection money!

17:56.590 --> 17:58.200
Ask them if you don't believe me!

17:58.200 --> 17:59.550
What's that in your hand?

17:59.550 --> 18:00.960
Isn't that money?

18:01.750 --> 18:03.110
Come on, I... This is money.

18:03.110 --> 18:04.840
But it's not protection money.

18:07.350 --> 18:09.590
The Fans just lost their parents.

18:10.000 --> 18:12.330
There are only two poor orphan girls left.

18:12.350 --> 18:14.640
Don't do such a cruel thing.

18:15.030 --> 18:15.560
Don't...

18:16.030 --> 18:17.360
Don't do such...

18:17.400 --> 18:18.720
-a cruel thing!
-Grandma, stop hitting me!

18:18.720 --> 18:20.450
Do you even know the situation?

18:20.790 --> 18:22.960
Stop hitting me, Grandma!

18:23.070 --> 18:23.830
Grandma Jin.

18:24.720 --> 18:26.720
He really didn't
take any protection money from me.

18:26.720 --> 18:28.160
They're helping me sell pork.

18:28.160 --> 18:29.560
This is an honest living.

18:36.040 --> 18:37.000
Selling pork?

18:40.480 --> 18:41.400
Really?

18:42.480 --> 18:43.260
Really.

18:44.110 --> 18:45.570
They swept this floor, too.

18:45.570 --> 18:46.370
That's right.

18:46.590 --> 18:47.850
And the stove outside—

18:48.020 --> 18:49.540
they helped fix it, too.

18:52.000 --> 18:53.530
Everyone saw it, right?

18:54.920 --> 18:56.300
I guess so.

19:03.730 --> 19:04.930
My grandson...

19:05.160 --> 19:06.110
has grown up.

19:08.000 --> 19:11.150
My grandson used to be a good kid.

19:13.920 --> 19:17.100
Work hard and honestly from now on.

19:17.350 --> 19:19.640
Don't hold up Mrs. Fan's business.

19:19.720 --> 19:21.550
Grandma, just go home.

19:21.550 --> 19:23.200
You're holding up our business now, okay?

19:23.200 --> 19:24.880
-Alright, alright.
-Hurry up and go.

19:24.880 --> 19:25.510
Alright.

19:26.550 --> 19:27.110
I...

19:31.160 --> 19:32.740
Look at you.

19:33.030 --> 19:34.200
Work hard.

19:41.960 --> 19:43.990
My grandson has grown up.

19:44.680 --> 19:47.240
He won't do bad things anymore.

19:55.240 --> 19:56.300
Alright, alright.

20:00.350 --> 20:01.960
My grandma, honestly.

20:02.000 --> 20:02.830
I mean, look how old I am.

20:02.830 --> 20:04.560
She still treats me like a baby.

20:04.590 --> 20:07.920
If word gets out, how am I supposed to
survive on the streets?

20:08.610 --> 20:10.720
Stop staring.
If you want to buy meat, hurry up.

20:10.720 --> 20:11.850
If not, get lost.

20:13.880 --> 20:14.750
Have a taste.

20:15.270 --> 20:17.550
You still have family in this world
who treats you so well.

20:17.550 --> 20:18.810
You should be content.

20:18.960 --> 20:20.270
You have hands and feet.

20:20.270 --> 20:21.920
Why not do some honest work?

20:23.400 --> 20:25.640
But I don't know any honest work to do.

20:27.030 --> 20:28.200
In a time like this,

20:28.880 --> 20:31.790
it's hard to be a bad guy,
but even harder to be a good one.

20:31.790 --> 20:32.750
Manwu's mother

20:33.110 --> 20:35.510
has been sick for years
and needs medicine.

20:36.160 --> 20:37.490
Mandi's younger sister

20:37.530 --> 20:39.880
was sent by her uncle
to do chores at a brothel.

20:39.880 --> 20:41.240
She's 6 months away from coming of age.

20:41.240 --> 20:42.520
If she isn't redeemed by then,

20:42.520 --> 20:44.580
she'll be forced into prostitution.

20:48.940 --> 20:49.630
Mancang...

20:50.920 --> 20:52.510
has been an orphan since childhood.

20:52.510 --> 20:54.160
He eats a lot but has no brains.

20:54.160 --> 20:56.360
He can't do any work. Who would want him?

20:57.960 --> 20:59.560
We want to be good people too,

21:00.240 --> 21:02.100
but in these years of endless war,

21:03.180 --> 21:04.710
good people can't survive.

21:12.350 --> 21:13.640
This meat is half fat and half lean.

21:13.640 --> 21:14.960
It's perfect for making dumplings.

21:14.960 --> 21:16.200
We charge 35 per jin.

21:16.230 --> 21:17.720
It's a little over two jin.

21:17.720 --> 21:19.400
I'll just count it as 2 jin for you,
alright?

21:19.400 --> 21:19.960
Sure.

21:20.110 --> 21:21.070
Let me weigh it for you.

21:21.070 --> 21:22.000
I have more here.

21:22.750 --> 21:24.010
Take care. Come again.

21:24.720 --> 21:26.110
Pork!

22:08.720 --> 22:10.780
Eat up. This is a meal for good people.

22:11.030 --> 22:12.090
It's not poisoned.

22:35.880 --> 22:37.140
This is today's wages.

22:37.270 --> 22:38.510
You only worked half a day,

22:38.510 --> 22:40.240
so you only get half a day's pay.

22:40.310 --> 22:41.370
I won't give extra,

22:42.070 --> 22:44.070
but I won't owe you anything either.

22:54.510 --> 22:56.770
Slow down. You eat like starving ghosts.

23:00.110 --> 23:00.920
Mrs. Fan.

23:06.790 --> 23:07.590
Um...

23:08.240 --> 23:10.440
Can we come help in the future?

23:16.270 --> 23:17.310
If you need food

23:17.440 --> 23:19.240
and want to work, you're welcome.

23:19.240 --> 23:20.290
But if you do anything bad,

23:20.290 --> 23:21.290
I won't be polite.

23:36.790 --> 23:38.850
It's Wang's on Middle Street, right?

23:39.640 --> 23:40.270
Yes.

23:43.550 --> 23:45.010
Are you going for revenge?

23:45.670 --> 23:46.590
Mrs. Yin!

23:47.000 --> 23:49.160
Keep an eye on the shop for me. Thanks.

23:47.090 --> 23:49.100
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

23:51.240 --> 23:51.920
Okay!

23:59.520 --> 24:01.050
We can't be disloyal.

24:01.120 --> 24:01.940
Follow her.

24:07.160 --> 24:09.590
No wonder those hooligans listen to her.

24:10.790 --> 24:12.610
She's the boss of them!

24:14.000 --> 24:14.750
Sir,

24:15.070 --> 24:16.200
this much money...

24:16.220 --> 24:19.240
if you spend it all on rice, flour,
salt, oil, sauce, and vinegar,

24:19.240 --> 24:20.870
one cart won't hold it all.

24:21.110 --> 24:22.370
Then add another cart.

24:23.030 --> 24:23.960
Alright.

24:23.870 --> 24:26.570
[Fan Erniu's residence
on the east section of Xigu Lane]

24:24.190 --> 24:25.680
Add 10 more jars of good wine,

24:25.680 --> 24:27.610
the kind suitable for the elderly.

24:27.680 --> 24:29.270
Also some tea and pastries.

24:29.400 --> 24:30.400
Send them to this address.

24:30.400 --> 24:31.240
No problem.

24:34.920 --> 24:35.520
By the way,

24:36.110 --> 24:38.920
do you have any ointment for chapped skin?

24:39.240 --> 24:40.200
Yes, we do.

24:41.680 --> 24:44.070
We have the best clam oil.

24:46.000 --> 24:48.110
Newly arrived. Take a look.

24:52.820 --> 24:53.880
I'll take them all.

24:55.600 --> 24:56.470
Okay, sir.

24:59.270 --> 25:01.590
Where did you get your wrist guards?

25:02.720 --> 25:04.720
Do they have ones suitable for ladies?

25:04.720 --> 25:06.050
Sir, you must be joking.

25:06.590 --> 25:07.640
Men

25:07.750 --> 25:09.480
use these

25:09.720 --> 25:11.000
for hard labor.

25:11.200 --> 25:13.070
Why would a girl need them?

25:13.640 --> 25:15.300
You can't find them anywhere.

25:17.270 --> 25:19.090
Where's Mrs. Fan going?

25:19.550 --> 25:20.830
She looks furious.

25:21.720 --> 25:23.520
I heard she's going for revenge.

25:26.830 --> 25:27.910
What's going on?

25:27.960 --> 25:29.030
Haven't you heard?

25:29.030 --> 25:31.000
Wang's Braised Meat Shop
was jealous of her business

25:31.000 --> 25:33.430
and sent people to smash Fan's shop.

25:33.640 --> 25:36.570
See? Fan's sent people
to retaliate against Wang's.

25:37.200 --> 25:38.160
If anyone asks,

25:38.240 --> 25:40.510
just say Fan Erniu deposited money
in your shop

25:40.510 --> 25:43.240
to be exchanged for New Year's goods
before the holiday.

25:43.240 --> 25:44.040
Alright, sir.

25:45.510 --> 25:46.750
Such a fine young lady,

25:46.750 --> 25:48.200
acting like a thug.

25:48.200 --> 25:49.400
Don't you agree, sir?

25:50.200 --> 25:51.810
Thank you. Thank you.

25:58.030 --> 25:59.460
Mrs. Fan, are you here to...

25:58.110 --> 25:58.570
[Wang's Braised Meat Shop]

26:00.440 --> 26:01.440
Gentlemen...

26:00.500 --> 26:02.950
[Wang's Braised Meat Shop]

26:01.440 --> 26:02.440
Move!

26:04.440 --> 26:06.160
Tell your shopkeeper to come out.

26:06.160 --> 26:07.880
He had the guts to smash my shop,

26:07.880 --> 26:09.810
but now he's hiding like a coward?

26:10.240 --> 26:11.440
What's going on here?

26:11.880 --> 26:12.790
Gentlemen,

26:12.920 --> 26:13.550
let's wait for our shopkeeper

26:13.550 --> 26:15.200
before we discuss anything.

26:15.240 --> 26:17.510
What's all the noise?

26:20.310 --> 26:21.110
Young Master.

26:29.700 --> 26:31.790
It was you who sent men to smash my shop?

26:31.790 --> 26:34.200
It was him. He gave us 5 taels of silver

26:34.200 --> 26:35.750
for smashing your stove.

26:36.400 --> 26:37.440
Who are you?

26:37.550 --> 26:39.630
Trying to deny it?

26:39.650 --> 26:41.880
We were drinking at the tavern

26:41.920 --> 26:43.570
when you approached us.

26:43.600 --> 26:44.400
You're still trying to deny it?

26:44.400 --> 26:45.110
Exactly.

26:45.200 --> 26:46.830
The tavern owner can testify too.

26:46.830 --> 26:49.120
Whoever denies it is a coward.

26:49.150 --> 26:50.780
The Young Master of Wang's,

26:50.920 --> 26:52.350
daring to smash my stove

26:52.350 --> 26:53.610
but afraid to admit it?

27:00.230 --> 27:02.100
It was just a stove.

27:03.110 --> 27:04.480
So what if I smashed it?

27:05.550 --> 27:06.680
What can you do to me?

27:08.790 --> 27:10.650
You're a girl.

27:11.310 --> 27:13.550
Instead of staying in your room
doing embroidery,

27:13.550 --> 27:15.920
you're out here trying to do business.

27:16.440 --> 27:18.970
Aren't you just asking
to be a laughingstock?

27:22.130 --> 27:23.610
Just because I'm a girl,

27:24.530 --> 27:26.190
I deserve to be bullied by you?

27:27.400 --> 27:28.920
I'm not bullying you.

27:29.510 --> 27:31.890
I feel sorry for you.

27:33.790 --> 27:34.590
Look at you.

27:35.590 --> 27:37.550
You're quite pretty.

27:38.000 --> 27:41.790
Why suffer for such a small business?

27:44.450 --> 27:46.090
I have plenty of money.

27:50.350 --> 27:51.080
Name a price.

27:52.240 --> 27:56.040
Sell me the recipe and yourself.
How about it?

28:01.470 --> 28:03.330
Who the hell do you think you are?

28:03.970 --> 28:06.030
You think you're worthy of my recipe?

28:10.870 --> 28:12.190
You bitch.

28:13.080 --> 28:16.850
You slept with that old Cook Li

28:17.030 --> 28:19.680
to cut off our business
with Yixiang Restaurant.

28:19.680 --> 28:21.510
And now you dared to come here?

28:21.510 --> 28:22.720
You butcher girl.

28:22.720 --> 28:24.320
How can you be so...

28:31.200 --> 28:32.750
Bravo! Bravo!

28:35.100 --> 28:37.310
When she beat us up earlier,

28:37.880 --> 28:39.610
she was actually holding back?

28:41.350 --> 28:42.110
Tell me.

28:43.270 --> 28:46.330
How did I steal your business
with Yixiang Restaurant?

28:46.880 --> 28:51.360
I-I heard that Wang's lost the business
with Yixiang Restaurant

28:51.640 --> 28:55.130
because Chef Li recommended your meat.

28:56.440 --> 28:57.500
So because of that,

28:57.750 --> 28:59.680
you're spreading rumors about me?

29:00.180 --> 29:01.070
I was wrong.

29:01.550 --> 29:02.440
You taught him a good lesson!

29:02.440 --> 29:03.160
Yes!

29:03.160 --> 29:05.270
It's lucky she's Fan Erniu's daughter.

29:05.270 --> 29:06.920
If it were another girl,

29:06.920 --> 29:08.380
being bullied like this,

29:08.530 --> 29:09.840
she would have no way...

29:09.840 --> 29:11.160
To deal with it.

29:11.160 --> 29:12.350
That's right.

29:12.350 --> 29:13.510
In my opinion,

29:13.510 --> 29:15.350
Wang's shop bullies customers
because it's big.

29:15.350 --> 29:16.200
Exactly.

29:16.310 --> 29:18.270
Back when the old man was around,

29:18.270 --> 29:20.000
their business was booming.

29:20.020 --> 29:22.210
Ever since Old Wang passed away,

29:22.240 --> 29:24.320
their braised meat
has gotten worse day by day.

29:24.320 --> 29:25.590
-Right?
-Yes!

29:25.810 --> 29:26.720
No wonder Yixiang Restaurant

29:26.720 --> 29:28.110
stopped doing business with him.

29:28.110 --> 29:28.910
Serves him right!

29:28.910 --> 29:31.840
If it were me,
I wouldn't do business with him either.

29:32.410 --> 29:34.700
If you dare to spread rumors

29:34.750 --> 29:36.720
and ruin a woman's reputation again,

29:36.720 --> 29:38.260
be careful—

29:40.790 --> 29:42.450
this knife of mine has no eyes.

29:42.850 --> 29:43.920
Got it.

29:56.750 --> 29:58.430
-You bastard!
-Young Master!

29:59.680 --> 30:01.240
Today, I…

30:02.180 --> 30:03.940
[Wang's Braised Meat Shop]

30:04.720 --> 30:07.350
[Liuji Sugar Shop]

30:07.450 --> 30:10.030
[Wang's Braised Meat Shop]

30:13.240 --> 30:14.240
Let me see you off.

30:15.220 --> 30:19.310
[Liuji Sugar Shop]

30:26.830 --> 30:28.830
That's Changyu from the Fan family?

30:30.510 --> 30:31.350
Exactly.

30:33.890 --> 30:34.690
Interesting.

30:35.220 --> 30:37.680
I didn't expect her to be so rough,
like a man.

30:38.880 --> 30:39.550
Let's go.

30:40.480 --> 30:41.070
Let's go.

30:50.110 --> 30:51.310
Your injury hasn't fully healed yet.

30:51.310 --> 30:52.640
Why did you come to town?

30:53.640 --> 30:54.970
Just came to have a look.

30:55.200 --> 30:56.660
I heard you went to Wang's,

30:56.830 --> 30:58.110
so I came to pick you up.

30:58.790 --> 30:59.720
How did it go?

31:00.510 --> 31:02.440
I hadn't even started hitting anyone yet.

31:02.440 --> 31:03.920
I just kicked his table,

31:04.040 --> 31:05.500
and he was scared to death.

31:05.510 --> 31:06.200
Then he...

31:08.960 --> 31:10.360
Why did you stop talking?

31:11.440 --> 31:12.160
Do you...

31:12.510 --> 31:14.910
think I'm vulgar too?

31:17.750 --> 31:19.300
You bastard!

31:33.590 --> 31:35.020
Only those with enough to eat
and a roof over their heads

31:35.020 --> 31:36.550
worry whether their actions

31:36.450 --> 31:38.650
♪ The scenery is as clear as me ♪

31:36.550 --> 31:37.890
are crude or refined.

31:38.440 --> 31:40.240
For people who spend all their energy
just to survive,

31:39.720 --> 31:40.690
♪ With very pale colors ♪

31:40.690 --> 31:42.560
no one has the right to judge them.

31:41.720 --> 31:44.560
♪ Just like the outline in the mirror ♪

31:45.140 --> 31:47.480
♪ I think that's me, being naive ♪

31:47.510 --> 31:50.030
In the past, my father wouldn't let me
use force in front of outsiders.

31:48.380 --> 31:49.700
♪ Unlocking my heart ♪

31:50.540 --> 31:54.700
♪ I hid you in my soul ♪

31:51.400 --> 31:53.000
My mother was even stricter.

31:53.310 --> 31:55.440
She wouldn't even let me butcher pigs.

31:55.510 --> 31:57.590
She said if a girl knows
how to do these things,

31:57.590 --> 31:58.640
people would gossip,

31:58.070 --> 32:00.540
♪ The moon is as quiet as me ♪

32:00.550 --> 32:02.440
and that if I marry Song Yan
in the future,

32:01.340 --> 32:02.950
♪ The light shines ♪

32:02.440 --> 32:03.730
even if he doesn't mind,

32:03.640 --> 32:06.380
♪ It illuminates
the turbulence in my heart ♪

32:04.550 --> 32:06.810
others will still gossip behind my back.

32:06.830 --> 32:09.440
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

32:08.270 --> 32:09.600
Later, my parents died.

32:10.060 --> 32:11.800
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

32:10.920 --> 32:12.100
To make a living,

32:12.250 --> 32:17.130
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

32:12.750 --> 32:15.210
I had no choice
but to start butchering pigs.

32:15.420 --> 32:18.160
I even used a stick
to teach people a lesson a few times.

32:18.160 --> 32:19.350
Now, people in town

32:19.350 --> 32:21.250
probably all think I'm a she-devil.

32:19.660 --> 32:20.730
♪ I pray that our love ♪

32:20.760 --> 32:23.450
♪ Will never end ♪

32:22.770 --> 32:24.930
A gambling house even sent me an offer,

32:24.120 --> 32:25.000
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

32:25.020 --> 32:27.400
♪ For a lifetime ♪

32:25.510 --> 32:27.790
saying if I don't butcher pigs
in the future,

32:27.790 --> 32:29.070
I can go help them collect debts.

32:28.030 --> 32:32.120
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

32:31.030 --> 32:32.290
Then go collect debts.

32:32.590 --> 32:35.960
♪ So what if we encounter difficulties? ♪

32:33.270 --> 32:33.960
Really?

32:35.350 --> 32:37.060
You're encouraging me to do that?

32:36.970 --> 32:37.900
♪ I pray that our love
will not be like sand ♪

32:37.240 --> 32:39.320
I'm telling you
not to fear people's words.

32:37.920 --> 32:40.380
♪ Slipping into the sea ♪

32:40.680 --> 32:42.200
Spreading rumors and slandering

32:41.710 --> 32:42.650
♪ I'd rather use this life ♪

32:42.310 --> 32:43.680
costs nothing

32:42.670 --> 32:45.110
♪ To guard our love forever ♪

32:44.110 --> 32:45.640
but causes great harm,

32:45.680 --> 32:47.030
especially to women.

32:45.820 --> 32:49.710
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

32:47.350 --> 32:48.810
You have to make them hurt,

32:49.240 --> 32:50.780
hurt more than the victim,

32:50.190 --> 32:58.380
♪ Why do we need
to seek cause and effect ♪

32:51.240 --> 32:52.550
to set things right.

32:55.900 --> 32:57.820
Set things right?

32:58.000 --> 32:59.670
What does that mean?

33:03.350 --> 33:04.030
Guess.

33:03.490 --> 33:07.860
♪ Clear and quiet ♪

33:05.030 --> 33:05.880
I don't know.

33:07.030 --> 33:07.750
Guess again.

33:07.750 --> 33:08.880
So what does it mean?

33:09.510 --> 33:11.570
Basically, it means...

33:09.770 --> 33:15.780
♪ As me ♪

33:20.830 --> 33:22.750
Changyu, eat. Zheng, eat.

33:25.200 --> 33:26.470
Where did this oil...

33:26.830 --> 33:29.240
and all these things come from?

33:29.310 --> 33:30.880
Father bought them.

33:31.480 --> 33:32.680
Don't talk nonsense.

33:33.310 --> 33:35.310
Changning isn't talking nonsense.

33:35.400 --> 33:37.640
I was confused seeing so many things too.

33:37.640 --> 33:40.960
The clerk said your father saved the money
at their place months ago

33:40.960 --> 33:43.310
to exchange it all for New Year goods,
which would be delivered here.

33:43.310 --> 33:45.370
Where did my father get so much money?

33:47.270 --> 33:48.720
Was it really my father?

33:48.790 --> 33:50.830
Yes, someone named Fan Erniu.

33:50.830 --> 33:52.680
See? It can't be fake.

33:53.310 --> 33:53.960
Who in these days

33:53.960 --> 33:57.690
would be foolish enough to deliver goods
for someone else for free?

33:58.480 --> 34:00.010
Yan Zheng, don't you agree?

34:01.160 --> 34:01.750
Yes.

34:03.150 --> 34:05.300
Besides, just this amount of stuff

34:05.440 --> 34:06.900
isn't that unusual, is it?

34:10.080 --> 34:11.580
Just?

34:13.190 --> 34:15.610
Changyu, look. There's also this.

34:18.760 --> 34:19.920
Clam oil?

34:20.030 --> 34:21.370
The food is fine,

34:21.550 --> 34:23.610
but why did he buy this useless stuff?

34:23.920 --> 34:25.000
Which shop is it from?

34:25.000 --> 34:25.860
I'll return it.

34:26.030 --> 34:27.030
Don't return it.

34:27.630 --> 34:30.110
Father must have felt sorry
for your chapped hands

34:30.110 --> 34:31.639
and prepared it for you.

34:31.710 --> 34:33.500
Our father wouldn't be so silly

34:33.530 --> 34:35.060
to buy such useless things.

34:35.400 --> 34:36.960
I'll return it and buy you candy.

34:36.960 --> 34:37.630
Wait.

34:43.230 --> 34:44.230
Once you use it...

34:45.920 --> 34:47.210
you can't return it.

34:51.920 --> 34:53.510
If you like it, take it and use it.

34:53.510 --> 34:54.370
I don't like it.

34:54.550 --> 34:56.360
Then why did you use it?

34:57.960 --> 35:00.220
Now that it's used, it can't be returned.

35:01.580 --> 35:04.930
Silly girl, your husband cares about you

35:05.030 --> 35:07.090
and wants you to keep it for yourself.

35:44.480 --> 35:45.880
Since it's already used,

35:47.160 --> 35:48.940
I'll just use it.

35:59.030 --> 36:00.690
Buying these useless things,

36:01.870 --> 36:03.800
I wonder what Father was thinking.

36:06.280 --> 36:07.230
Your father

36:08.080 --> 36:09.610
was thinking exactly that.

36:30.590 --> 36:31.480
Tomorrow,

36:32.430 --> 36:34.160
the court will begin the trial.

36:35.190 --> 36:36.790
Do you need me to go with you?

36:37.960 --> 36:38.630
No need.

36:39.110 --> 36:40.720
Mr. Zhao and the others will be with me.

36:40.720 --> 36:41.920
You have a leg injury,

36:41.950 --> 36:43.480
so you can't kneel for long.

36:45.480 --> 36:47.440
I've remembered everything you taught me.

36:47.440 --> 36:48.300
I'm not afraid.

36:58.190 --> 36:59.990
Knives are not allowed in court.

37:02.920 --> 37:04.190
This is my livelihood.

37:04.190 --> 37:05.790
Forbidden means forbidden!

37:15.070 --> 37:17.980
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence]

37:23.030 --> 37:24.890
[Government]

37:29.660 --> 37:32.270
Why haven't I seen Fan Daniu and his wife?

37:33.070 --> 37:34.470
Did they forget the time?

37:36.960 --> 37:38.640
Those two heartless people.

37:39.000 --> 37:41.320
I'd believe it
if they forgot their parents' names.

37:41.320 --> 37:42.800
But forgetting about fighting for a house?

37:42.800 --> 37:44.200
I don't think they would.

37:45.030 --> 37:45.670
True.

37:46.840 --> 37:48.280
Then where did they go?

37:49.280 --> 37:50.680
They are the plaintiffs.

37:59.000 --> 38:03.720
[Righteousness]

38:02.480 --> 38:03.230
Start the trial.

38:03.230 --> 38:06.630
Beware!

38:07.000 --> 38:10.000
Bring the plaintiffs
and the defendants to the court.

38:10.490 --> 38:12.660
[Government]

38:17.170 --> 38:18.950
Who is kneeling down there?

38:19.190 --> 38:20.790
I am Fan Changyu.

38:20.880 --> 38:22.800
Greetings, Your Honor!

38:29.990 --> 38:32.550
[Righteousness]

38:30.400 --> 38:32.630
Where is the plaintiff, Fan Daniu?

38:40.670 --> 38:41.760
Preposterous!

38:42.400 --> 38:44.190
I have been a judge for so long,

38:44.550 --> 38:48.210
but this is the first time
I've seen a plaintiff absent from court.

38:50.150 --> 38:51.360
Please calm down, My Lord.

38:51.360 --> 38:53.110
Fan Daniu must have a reason

38:53.110 --> 38:54.550
for being late.

38:54.670 --> 38:57.330
Why not send a police runner
to his home to check?

38:57.510 --> 39:00.640
This will show your fairness
and impartiality, My Lord.

39:01.510 --> 39:02.150
Granted.

39:03.230 --> 39:04.490
Well, Constable Wang,

39:04.590 --> 39:07.190
send someone
to the Fan family in East Village.

39:07.440 --> 39:08.000
Yes.

39:09.030 --> 39:11.360
Court is adjourned for now.

39:11.800 --> 39:12.360
Dismiss.

39:12.960 --> 39:13.960
It's dismissed just like that?

39:13.960 --> 39:14.620
Yeah.

39:15.480 --> 39:16.230
Come on. Make way.

39:16.230 --> 39:17.800
Wang, what's going on?

39:18.150 --> 39:18.950
It's nothing.

39:19.070 --> 39:19.550
Come.

39:24.360 --> 39:27.130
Did Changyu catch Fan Daniu?

39:27.280 --> 39:28.630
Why would she catch him?

39:29.030 --> 39:31.030
Changyu is already married.

39:31.030 --> 39:34.230
It's an obviously winning lawsuit.
That wouldn't be necessary.

39:34.230 --> 39:34.760
Besides,

39:34.760 --> 39:36.870
she stayed at home all last night.

39:37.230 --> 39:38.800
Okay. I'm relieved then.

39:42.140 --> 39:45.260
[Government]

39:45.370 --> 39:48.430
[Righteousness]

39:48.530 --> 39:51.810
[Qingping County Government Office]

39:51.910 --> 39:55.730
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence]

40:02.480 --> 40:03.410
Start the trial.

40:03.430 --> 40:07.260
Beware!

40:07.590 --> 40:10.220
Your Honor,
I have a matrilocal husband now.

40:10.240 --> 40:13.240
According to the law,
I can inherit the family estate.

40:16.070 --> 40:17.590
We have waited for 2 hours.

40:17.800 --> 40:19.200
We won't wait any longer.

40:19.230 --> 40:21.290
Since the plaintiff has not arrived,

40:21.480 --> 40:23.230
I now pronounce

40:23.400 --> 40:25.260
that the defendant wins the case!

40:25.920 --> 40:27.280
My Lord!

40:29.000 --> 40:30.070
My Lord!

40:30.840 --> 40:32.000
My Lord!

40:35.800 --> 40:40.400
You must seek justice for me, My Lord!

40:44.880 --> 40:45.800
My Lord,

40:46.670 --> 40:49.760
you must seek justice for me!

40:59.670 --> 41:01.400
You jinx!

41:02.150 --> 41:03.880
To steal this house,

41:04.000 --> 41:06.670
you actually killed your uncle!
